abstract: Matt Jones shoots three-under-par 68 to take three-stroke lead after two rounds at Australian Open in Sydney.
lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth and Adam Scott went in opposite directions in the second round of the Australian Open in Sydney, while Matt Jones shot a three-under-par 68 to take a three-stroke lead.
